{"tid":2108284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有幾多人真心相信35+？","createTime":"2020-07-14T12:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T19:05:31.000Z","uid":88743,"like":77,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca9f8a987ddbe462700fce83a1e8229ba8a2259","tid":2108284,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"【３５＋最強後盾】入黎話你知點解我地要團結一致３５＋　香港唯一出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2107354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2107354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前開po 叫人支持35+ 完全無人理<br />\n<br />\n其實有無人知35+最主要目的係為乜<br />\n而家好似每個人理解都唔同<br />\n<br />\n有人話要令中共DQ付出更大政治代價<br />\n有人就話要入立會全面否決議案<br />\n完全兩個approach, 令到一班人見國安法就縮，一班就追住國安法黎屌<br />\n<br />\n其實大家目標係乜？<br />\n大家係點理解<br />\n正評/負評左既 可否講下你諗既approach 可行性同預期有咩障礙？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令中共DQ付出更大政治代價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要入立會全面否決議案"},{"pid":"d7bcc4aa4782c3ebed75eb2f5f71ba22834f81c5","tid":2108284,"uid":74368,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:14:22.000Z","msg":"Hope for best,<br />\nprepare for the worst."},{"pid":"a392108bdb36d9767e6bb1da153820fc65817b8a","tid":2108284,"uid":259246,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"唔信 不過盡做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce56b104bbc9f84df1a785d9af92204ab721d000","tid":2108284,"uid":144718,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"完全無相信過35+ <br />\n<br />\n我唔會投票但支持亦都鼓勵其他人投票，當促成到35+時香港人就會明中共根本就唔撚怕同你耍無賴，搲爛塊面。"},{"pid":"011f8c9f8e2f45b8df3e77515f0b66e0183e0da2","tid":2108284,"uid":284001,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"唔信 不過照做"},{"pid":"ef4688f2ffe6641ab10ea3e68f94da13837892a7","tid":2108284,"uid":323588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime