like":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"應該問 <br />\n<br />\n立法會仲有咩用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"作用就係打破香港人嘅幻想"},{"pid":"0c42d804d685045136dcfa336f5c67750b6c2c37","tid":2108284,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"de2e7b6931aec905a0f86038347c237d90270ef2","tid":2108284,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"只可以講香港人淨係得番投票可以做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"你咁講就錯<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係因為有投票<br />\n心力放哂係投票<br />\n無人帶頭搞遊行<br />\n所以少左街頭抗爭?<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得之前係每星期一次<br />\n每星期有人入紙<br />\n而家呢？無人申請<br />\n因為全部搞緊選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔批都可以申請架？好似岑子杰七一入紙咁<br />\n不過暫時一定唔會啦<br />\n好似上面我講離場抗議一樣<br />\n收割左先 呢兩個月 唔好搞咁多野 出咁多uncertainty 陣間搞個遊行就俾人捉又DQ 咪仆街 而家<br />\n岑子杰最高票喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過左選舉先搞啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七二一就到啦<br />\n咪又係無聲無氣<br />\n<br />\n所以香港人群<br />\n其實只係俾搞社運既人既一舉一動舞緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時又昆到一班人認為香港人只係得投票可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就是被騙成相信選舉既成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08068f3c800c780be61c00a5deca515410f6e496","tid":2108284,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"797015c688d7aad00fee14c5cb931fa0a6925d14","tid":2108284,"uid":264325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:13:28.000Z","msg":"一路都冇諗過可以35+<br />\n有26-28席已經算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im